---
import SiteLayout from "../../layouts/SiteLayout.astro";
---

<SiteLayout title="Landlord & Tenant | ImmediateLawyerHelp.com">
<!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="heroBg" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div class="container heroInner">
      <div class="heroCard">
        <h1>Landlord &amp; Tenant</h1>
        <p class="heroSub">
          Housing disputes often involve notices, deadlines, and local rules that vary by city and state.
          Choose a path below, or describe what’s happening to continue.
        </p>

        <form id="heroSearchForm" class="heroSearch" autocomplete="off">
          <input
            id="issueInput"
            type="text"
            placeholder="Briefly describe your landlord/tenant issue…"
            aria-label="Describe your landlord/tenant issue"
          />
          <button type="submit">Get Started</button>
        </form>

        <div class="heroBadges">
          <span>Time-sensitive</span><span class="sep">•</span>
          <span>Confidential</span><span class="sep">•</span>
          <span>Independent attorneys</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Article -->
  <section class="section sectionTight">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card">
        <article class="ltArticle">
          <h2 class="cardTitle">Common landlord and tenant issues</h2>
          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px; line-height:1.65; max-width:78ch;">
            Landlord-tenant matters can turn on written notices, lease terms, payment history, and the condition of the property.
            The topics below are organized by perspective and link to dedicated pages (coming soon).
          </p>

          <section class="ltSection" id="if-tenant">
            <h3 class="ltH"><a class="ltTitleLink" href="/landlord-tenant/tenant/">If Tenant</a></h3>
            <div class="ltImage">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522708323590-d24dbb6b0267?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <p class="guideMeta ltBlurb">
              Tenant issues may include eviction notices, rent disputes, unsafe living conditions, repairs, security deposits, and lease violations.
              These cases often depend on written notices, documentation of requests, photos, and timelines.
              Because rules vary locally, understanding what notices mean and what deadlines apply is often the first step.
            </p>
            <a class="ltLearn" href="/landlord-tenant/tenant/">Learn more →</a>
          </section>

          <section class="ltSection" id="if-landlord">
            <h3 class="ltH"><a class="ltTitleLink" href="/landlord-tenant/landlord/">If Landlord</a></h3>
            <div class="ltImage">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560518883-ce09059eeffa?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1600&q=60" alt="" loading="lazy" />
            </div>
            <p class="guideMeta ltBlurb">
              Landlord issues may involve nonpayment, lease enforcement, property access, damage, holdover tenants, and eviction procedure.
              Many situations require proper notices and documented compliance with local process.
              A quick review of the lease, payment history, and notices already sent can clarify viable next steps.
            </p>
            <a class="ltLearn" href="/landlord-tenant/landlord/">Learn more →</a>
          </section>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Keep sideSearchForm present -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container twoCol">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="cardTitle">Not sure which applies?</h2>
        <p class="muted" style="line-height:1.6; max-width:72ch;">
          Describe your housing issue and we’ll route you to the right next step.
        </p>

        <form id="sideSearchForm" class="sideSearch" autocomplete="off">
          <input type="text" placeholder="Describe your issue…" aria-label="Describe your issue" />
          <button type="submit" aria-label="Search">→</button>
        </form>
      </div>

      <aside class="card">
        <h2 class="cardTitle">Notes</h2>
        <ul class="bullets">
          <li>Information on this site is not legal advice.</li>
          <li>Using this site does not create an attorney-client relationship.</li>
          <li>Independent attorneys may have different availability and policies.</li>
        </ul>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    /* Landlord/Tenant page-specific styling: restrained images, article rhythm */
    .ltArticle .ltSection{
      padding: 18px 0 34px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .ltArticle .ltSection:last-of-type{
      border-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .ltH{
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }
    .ltTitleLink{
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .ltTitleLink:hover{
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    .ltImage{
      margin: 12px 0 18px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      overflow: hidden;
      max-width: 62%;
    }
    .ltImage img{
      width: 100%;
      height: 140px;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
      filter: saturate(.9) contrast(.95);
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px){
      .ltImage{ max-width: 100%; }
    }
    .ltBlurb{
      margin-top: 10px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 78ch;
    }
    .ltLearn{
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.10);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 650;
    }
    .ltLearn:hover{
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
  </style>
</SiteLayout>
